articles.author: Adam Cooper
articles.title: F1 drivers want Las Vegas track surface to match "gold standard" Jeddah - Autosport
articles.description: Formula 1 drivers have expressed disappointment in the slippery track surface in Las Vegas, with several contrasting it with what George Russell termed the “gold standard” of Saudi Arabia's Jeddah street circuit.
